---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import TopNav from '../../components/TopNav.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
import RelatedPages from '../../components/RelatedPages.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';

import { getSidebarGroups } from '../../data/sidebar-config.ts';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, '');

const sidebarGroups = getSidebarGroups('progression');
---
<BaseLayout title="Progression Guide | MITE:BE Wiki" description="MITE:BE progression from flint age to Ender Dragon. Detailed guide across 7 phases.">
  <Header />
  <TopNav currentPage="progression" />
  <div class="container">
    <Sidebar groups={sidebarGroups} />
    <main class="content">

<div id="prog-summary" style="margin-bottom:16px; font-size:.9em; color:var(--text2);"></div>
<script is:inline>
(function() {
  var pages = ['early-game','furnaces','metal-ages','underground','late-game','nether','endgame'];
  var labels = { hu: 'fejezet befejezve', en: 'chapters completed', ru: 'глав завершено' };
  try {
    var done = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('mite-wiki-progress') || '[]');
    var count = pages.filter(function(p) { return done.includes(p); }).length;
    var el = document.getElementById('prog-summary');
    if (el && count > 0) {
      var lang = (localStorage.getItem('mite-wiki-lang') || 'hu');
      var label = labels[lang] || labels.hu;
      el.innerHTML = '<span style="color:#4caf50">✓ ' + count + '/7</span> ' + label;
    }
  } catch(e) {}
})();
</script>

<!-- ══ HUNGARIAN ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div data-lang="hu">
<h2 id="progression">Fejlődési Útmutató</h2>
<p>A MITE:BE progressziója lépésről lépésre halad — kovakortól az Ender-sárkányig. Válaszd ki a megfelelő szakaszt a bal oldali menüből vagy az alábbi kártyákból!</p>

<div class="prog-chapters">
  <div class="prog-tree">
    <span class="prog-node n-flint">🪨 Korai</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-flint">🔥 Kemence</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-copper">⚙️ Fémek</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-underground">⛏️ Föld</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-mithril">🌟 Késő</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-nether">🌋 Nether</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-adam">👑 Vége</span>
  </div>

  <div class="prog-chapters-grid">
    <a href={`${base}/progression/early-game/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🪨</div>
      <h3>1. Korai Játék</h3>
      <p>Első percek, kovakorszak, munkaasztal, szita. A nulláról indulsz — kovaszilánkkal és növényszállal.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/furnaces/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🔥</div>
      <h3>2. Kemencék & Olvasztás</h3>
      <p>Agyagkemence, tábortűz, keményített agyagkemence, öntőforma, első fémrúd olvasztása.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/metal-ages/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">⚙️</div>
      <h3>3. Fémkorszakok</h3>
      <p>Réz, ezüst, ötvözetek (bronz, ezüst-réz, szénacél), többblokkos kemence, vas, fémhierarchia.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/underground/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">⛏️</div>
      <h3>4. Földalatti Világ</h3>
      <p>Barlangok, Underground dimenzió, keménykő, ősi fém. Minimum vas felszerelés ajánlott.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/late-game/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🌟</div>
      <h3>5. Késői Játék</h3>
      <p>Mithril korszak, kétszájú üst, elementális obszidián — felkészülés az Alvilágra.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/nether/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🌋</div>
      <h3>6. Alvilág (Nether)</h3>
      <p>Portálok, Nether szörnyek, Blaze-rúd, adamantium olvasztás, Wither boss.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/endgame/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">👑</div>
      <h3>7. Végső Szakasz</h3>
      <p>Alapkőzet-zúzó, The End, Ender-sárkány legyőzése — a játék vége!</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ══ ENGLISH ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div data-lang="en">
<h2 id="progression">Progression Guide</h2>
<p>MITE:BE's progression moves step by step — from the flint age to the Ender Dragon. Choose a stage from the sidebar or the cards below!</p>

<div class="prog-chapters">
  <div class="prog-tree">
    <span class="prog-node n-flint">🪨 Early</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-flint">🔥 Furnaces</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-copper">⚙️ Metals</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-underground">⛏️ Underground</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-mithril">🌟 Late</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-nether">🌋 Nether</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-adam">👑 End</span>
  </div>

  <div class="prog-chapters-grid">
    <a href={`${base}/progression/early-game/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🪨</div>
      <h3>1. Early Game</h3>
      <p>First minutes, flint age, workbench, sieve. Starting from zero — with flint shards and plant fibers.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/furnaces/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🔥</div>
      <h3>2. Furnaces & Smelting</h3>
      <p>Clay furnace, campfire, hardened clay furnace, ingot mold, first metal smelting.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/metal-ages/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">⚙️</div>
      <h3>3. Metal Ages</h3>
      <p>Copper, silver, alloys (bronze, silver-copper, high-carbon steel), multiblock furnace, iron, metal hierarchy.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/underground/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">⛏️</div>
      <h3>4. Underground</h3>
      <p>Caves, Underground dimension, hardstone, ancient metal. Full iron gear strongly recommended.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/late-game/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🌟</div>
      <h3>5. Late Game</h3>
      <p>Mithril age, two-mouthed cauldron, elemental obsidian — preparing for the Nether.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/nether/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🌋</div>
      <h3>6. The Nether</h3>
      <p>Portals, Nether mobs, Blaze Rods, adamantium smelting, Wither boss.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/endgame/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">👑</div>
      <h3>7. Endgame</h3>
      <p>Bedrock Pulverizer, The End, defeating the Ender Dragon — game complete!</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<!-- ══ RUSSIAN ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div data-lang="ru">
<h2 id="progression">Руководство по прогрессии</h2>
<p>Прогрессия MITE:BE идёт шаг за шагом — от кремниевой эпохи до Дракона Края. Выберите этап в боковом меню или из карточек ниже!</p>

<div class="prog-chapters">
  <div class="prog-tree">
    <span class="prog-node n-flint">🪨 Начало</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-flint">🔥 Печи</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-copper">⚙️ Металлы</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-underground">⛏️ Земля</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-mithril">🌟 Поздно</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-nether">🌋 Незер</span>
    <span class="prog-arrow">→</span>
    <span class="prog-node n-adam">👑 Конец</span>
  </div>

  <div class="prog-chapters-grid">
    <a href={`${base}/progression/early-game/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🪨</div>
      <h3>1. Начало игры</h3>
      <p>Первые минуты, кремниевая эпоха, верстак, сито.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/furnaces/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🔥</div>
      <h3>2. Печи и плавка</h3>
      <p>Глиняная печь, костёр, форма для слитков, первый металл.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/metal-ages/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">⚙️</div>
      <h3>3. Металлические эпохи</h3>
      <p>Медь, серебро, сплавы, многоблочная печь, железо.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/underground/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">⛏️</div>
      <h3>4. Подземный мир</h3>
      <p>Пещеры, подземное измерение, твердокамень, древний металл.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/late-game/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🌟</div>
      <h3>5. Поздняя игра</h3>
      <p>Мифрил, двуротый котёл, подготовка к Незеру.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/nether/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">🌋</div>
      <h3>6. Незер</h3>
      <p>Порталы, мобы Незера, адамант, босс Иссушитель.</p>
    </a>
    <a href={`${base}/progression/endgame/`} class="prog-chapter-card">
      <div class="card-icon">👑</div>
      <h3>7. Финал</h3>
      <p>Измельчитель бедрока, Край, победа над Драконом.</p>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
</div>

<RelatedPages
  prev={{
    href: `${base}/introduction/`,
    label: { hu: 'Bevezetés', en: 'Introduction', ru: 'Введение' }
  }}
  next={{
    href: `${base}/progression/early-game/`,
    label: { hu: 'Korai Játék', en: 'Early Game', ru: 'Начало игры' }
  }}
/>

    </main>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
